      "title": "Sri Lanka raises Rs.50 bln via T-bonds",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka raised 50 billion rupees via Treasury bonds at an auction on Thursday after calling bids for the same amount, data from the state debt office showed.",
        "20 billion rupees of 01 June 2025 bonds were sold at 28.45 percent after calling bids for 20 billion.",
        "30 billion rupees of\u00a001 May 2031\u00a0bonds were sold at 23.91 percent after calling bids for 30 billion. (Colombo/ July 28/2022)"
      ],
